name: Quantum - Usuahia(AR) <=> Hiroshima (JP)
description:
The work collects meteorological data from different cities around the world to dump them in real time. 

You can intervene in the play during the streaming twitch.tv/mettapana_av (see announcements on twitter).

Quantum is a generative artwork inspired by the random behavior of the universe.

Moon Edition is the first in the series.

Size: 1280x720
